WEBVTT

00:09:28.055 --> 00:09:30.794
Nowadays, we adults
have to guide our children

00:09:30.818 --> 00:09:33.276
through what is often for us
unfamiliar territory --

00:09:33.300 --> 00:09:35.319
territory much more inviting for them.

00:09:37.501 --> 00:09:40.569
It's impossible to find an answer

00:09:40.593 --> 00:09:43.641
without doing new things --
things that make us uncomfortable,

00:09:43.665 --> 00:09:45.151
things we're not used to.

00:09:47.581 --> 00:09:50.272
A lot of you may think it's easy for me,

00:09:50.296 --> 00:09:52.043
because I'm relatively young.

00:09:52.681 --> 00:09:54.161
And it used to be that way.

00:09:55.342 --> 00:09:56.502
Used to.

00:09:58.249 --> 00:10:00.115
Until last year,